"PROGRAM:  HorseRace\nCALLING SEQUENCE:  HorseRace[n]\nPARAMETERS:  \n     n \
- an integer\nSYNOPSIS:\n     - This program simulates n of the horse races \
described in Chapter 1.  The\n       program prints each race winner, and \
returns a list containing the percentage of\n       times each horse won. \n\
RETURNED VALUES:\n     -  a list containing the number of times each horse \
won\nLOCATION:\n     Folder:  Chapter 1\n     File:       \
\"HorseRace.Chpt1.mat\"",
  FontFamily->"Helvetica"]], "Text",
